===Etymology===
From {{L.}} '''explōsiōnis''', genitive form of '''[[explosio|explōsio]]''' < '''[[explodo|explōdo]]''' "I drive out by clapping" < '''[[ex-#Latin|ex-]]''' and '''[[plodo|plōdo]]''' "I clap or strike"

