===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[violent]] release of [[energy]] (sometimes [[mechanical]], [[nuclear]], or [[chemical]].)
# A [[burst]]ing due to [[pressure]].
# The [[sound]] of an explosion.
# A sudden [[increase]].
# A sudden [[outburst]].

